one day meteorite will fall from the sky and in their wake everything die the world around us will go its way one day , one day I will wait , either way I will wait , either way body turn into dust building into rust the land give in to the sea life float into space scatter without a trace and all you can think about be me I will wait for you ( I will wait , I will wait for you ) building come crash down fire be all around I will wait , I will wait for you keep your head hold up high I will be somewhere in the shape that twist the sky I know soon we will reunite your embrace will surely keep us alive C'est un été rouge C'est un été rouge C'est un été rouge C'est un été rouge ( I will wait for you ) C'est un été rouge C'est un été rouge ( I will wait for you ) C'est un été rouge C'est un ... I will wait for you ( I will wait , I will wait for you ) I will wait for you ( I will wait , I will wait for you ) building come crash down fire be all around I will wait , I will wait for you stroll on blacken ground what be lose , will never be find I will wait , I will wait _______________________________________ name été rouge ( feat . dead astronaut ) Artist Diana Gitallog , Pacifico